# FinanceOS — Production Environment Variables
# NEXT_PUBLIC_* vars are inlined at build time into the client bundle.
# The Supabase anon key is a PUBLISHABLE key (like Stripe's pk_) — it is
# scoped to authenticated operations only via Row-Level Security (RLS).
# It is NOT a secret key. The service_role key is never exposed here.

